This directory contains additional scripts which are triggered whenever
a testing process completes.

The hook dispatcher file 'hooks.hk' contains the list of the hooks
to trigger.

Note that a crontab 'hooks.cron' is provided and should be loaded in order
for the 'cron.py' script to be triggered once a day.

